<plot>Rebecca Daniels lives two lives. In one she is a civil servant and a loving wife and mother. In the other she is a highly trained foreign operative, planted in deep cover in the heart of the United States intelligence community. When her cover is blown and she needs to be extracted, she faces losing the life she has built for herself. In the end, she must make a choice between duty to her country and her love for her family.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?117269</url></doc>
